articleTitle: Oska zu Gast beim KURIER Talk
articleTitleTranslated: Oska as a guest at the KURIER Talk
articleContent: Die heimische Singer-Songwriterin im Gespräch über ihre EP "Honeymoon Phase", das Künstlerleben in Corona-Zeiten und das Musikbusiness.
articleContentTranslated: The local singer-songwriter in conversation about her EP "Honeymoon Phase", the artist life in Corona times and the music business.
